---
/**
 * 关于我们 - Hero 区块组件
 *
 * @description 包含页面标题、简介、品牌使命/愿景卡片和联系信息
 */
---

<!-- Hero 容器 -->
<section
  id="hero-section"
  class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-b-[40px] bg-gradient-to-r from-dark via-dark-900 to-dark pb-20 pt-24 md:rounded-b-[60px] md:pb-28 md:pt-32 lg:rounded-b-[72px] lg:pb-36 lg:pt-40"
>
  <div class="content-container">
    <!-- 主标题 -->
    <h1
      class="mb-6 text-center text-[40px] font-bold leading-tight text-white md:mb-8 md:text-[52px] lg:text-[60px]"
    >
      关于我们
    </h1>

    <!-- 简介文本 -->
    <p
      class="mx-auto mb-10 max-w-[784px] text-center text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-light-text md:mb-12 md:text-[17px] lg:text-[19px]"
    >
      VSTAR隶属于VS金融集团，是一家专注于金融科技领域的创新企业。我们的创始团队由一批来自全球顶尖科技公司与金融机构的资深专家组成，他们怀揣着一个共同的愿景：利用科技力量，重塑金融行业的服务模式与安全标准。如今，VSTAR已成长为一家在全球享有盛誉的品牌。
    </p>

    <!-- 查看详情按钮 -->
    <div class="mb-14 flex justify-center lg:mb-16">
      <a
        href="#details"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary px-10 py-3.5 text-[15px] font-medium text-white transition-colors hover:bg-primary-dark md:px-12 md:py-4 md:text-[16px]"
      >
        查看详情
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- 品牌卡片组 -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-3 md:gap-6 lg:gap-7">
      <!-- 联系我们卡片 -->
      <div
        class="bg-white/8 hover:bg-white/12 flex flex-col justify-between rounded-[15px] p-5 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all md:rounded-[20px] md:p-6 lg:rounded-[22px] lg:p-7"
      >
        <div class="mb-6">
          <div class="mb-5">
            <!-- 邮箱图标 -->
            <div
              class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-white/10"
            >
              <svg
                class="h-5 w-5 text-white/70"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p
            class="border-white/8 mb-2 border-b pb-4 text-[13px] text-light-text md:text-[14px] lg:text-[15px]"
          >
            support@vstar.com
          </p>
        </div>
        <a
          href="mailto:support@vstar.com"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-white px-5 py-2.5 text-[13px] font-medium text-dark transition-all hover:bg-white/95 hover:shadow-lg md:text-[14px] lg:py-3"
        >
          联系我们
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- 品牌使命卡片 -->
      <div
        class="bg-white/8 hover:bg-white/12 rounded-[15px] p-5 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all md:rounded-[20px] md:p-6 lg:rounded-[22px] lg:p-7"
      >
        <div class="mb-5">
          <!-- 使命图标 -->
          <div
            class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-white/10"
          >
            <svg
              class="h-5 w-5 text-white/70"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3
          class="mb-3 text-[18px] font-semibold text-white md:text-[20px] lg:text-[22px]"
        >
          品牌使命
        </h3>
        <p
          class="text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-light-text md:text-[14px] lg:text-[15px]"
        >
          以创新科技，构建更安全、更高效的金融技术基础设施
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 品牌愿景卡片 -->
      <div
        class="bg-white/8 hover:bg-white/12 rounded-[15px] p-5 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all md:rounded-[20px] md:p-6 lg:rounded-[22px] lg:p-7"
      >
        <div class="mb-5">
          <!-- 愿景图标 -->
          <div
            class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-white/10"
          >
            <svg
              class="h-5 w-5 text-white/70"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3
          class="mb-3 text-[18px] font-semibold text-white md:text-[20px] lg:text-[22px]"
        >
          品牌愿景
        </h3>
        <p
          class="text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-light-text md:text-[14px] lg:text-[15px]"
        >
          成为连接全球市场的、备受信赖的金融科技品牌
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
